<section class="pg-section" data-section="Your Rejuvenating Hydrafacial Keravive Experience">
  <h2 class="pg-h">Your Rejuvenating Hydrafacial Keravive Experience</h2>
  <p class="pg-text">This innovative scalp health treatment is designed to cleanse, exfoliate, nourish, and hydrate the scalp. It addresses common issues like dryness, clogged follicles, and poor circulation to promote healthier and fuller-looking hair for all skin and hair types.</p>
  <p class="pg-text">​HydraFacial’s proprietary Vortex Technology easily dislodges and removes impurities from the scalp and hair follicle. The Keravive Peptide Complex Solution delivers a hyper-concentrated blend of biomimetic growth factors and skin proteins that hydrate and nourish the scalp.</p>
  <h3 class="pg-h">CLEANSE + EXFOLIATE</h3>
  <p class="pg-text">Relaxing, painless suction and hydration removes dirt, oil, and dead skin flakes from the scalp. Deeply cleanses hair follicles of product build up.</p>
  <h3 class="pg-h">HYDRATE + NOURISH</h3>
  <p class="pg-text">HydraFacial Keravive Scalp Health Solution infuses a proprietary blend of biomimetic growth factors and skin proteins to promote a healthy scalp.</p>
  <h3 class="pg-h">EXTEND + ENHANCE</h3>
  <p class="pg-text">HydraFacial Keravive Scalp Health Take−Home Spray enhances the benefits of the in−office treatment &amp; delivers daily nourishment.</p>
  <a class="pg-btn" href="/hydrafacial-keravive">Schedule Now</a>
</section>

